            Temporary Initiation Stop discontinued&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="NewsUser">Errol 
            - 01-02-2001 at 11:33:11</span> 
            <br>
		  <span class="NewsTitleDescription">As you've probably noticed....</span>
		  </td>
