			I would like everyone to welcome to Aegis. Delph a warrior of the 42nd season, Minvardar a druid of the 43 season, and Zeril a cleric of the 19th season. Welcome to Aegis and I know you all will bring honor to our fine family.<br>
          </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
